# Documents

Place the following PDF files in this directory:

- `you_are_here.pdf` — YOU ARE HERE: Keep Existing (full framework)
- `you_are_here_v3_fillable.pdf` — Fillable blank template
- `forensic_absolution_v1.2.pdf` — Forensic Absolution framework
- `forge_math_complete.pdf` — Forge Math: Complete Sovereign Equations (100 equations)
- `forge_math_tier1_essential_eight.pdf` — Forge Math: The Essential Eight (8 core equations)
- `forge_math_tier2_professional_briefing.pdf` — Forge Math: Professional Briefing (23 equations with clinical data)
- `toolkit_readme.pdf` — THE YOU ARE HERE TOOLKIT: How To Use These Documents
